## ğŸ—ƒï¸ Database Tables

Below are the tables included in our schema:

- `brand` â€“ Stores product brand info  
- `product_category` â€“ Categories like clothing, electronics  
- `product` â€“ General product details  
- `product_image` â€“ URLs or references to product images  
- `color` â€“ Available color options  
- `size_category` â€“ Categories of sizes (e.g., clothing, shoes)  
- `size_option` â€“ Specific size values (e.g., S, M, L, 42)  
- `product_variation` â€“ Combines a product with a color  
- `product_item` â€“ A sellable item with a specific size and variation  
- `attribute_category` â€“ Groups of attributes (e.g., physical, technical)  
- `attribute_type` â€“ Data types for attributes (e.g., text, number, boolean)  
- `product_attribute` â€“ Custom attributes like material, weight, etc.

